{"tid":1569844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂 ] 今日行動 post  9.15英領集會 懶人包  一文睇晒","createTime":"2019-09-14T18:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T04:59:01.000Z","uid":101537,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"a528a636b62ba51f0486a3c1ab51c424b590b5ce","tid":1569844,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5NoYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5NoYN.jpg&h=6894a64b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地915自發請願係 12點開始，過程約1-1.5小時。 同上次一樣，9月15號屬個人自發排大隊去英國領事館 &quot;灰磚範圍&quot; 請願，太多人時記得有秩序地 &quot;等候&quot; 進入英領範圍, 千祈唔好行出馬路，唔好100%阻塞行人路，唔好阻塞對面香格里拉酒店門口，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔係路邊集會，係去英領既人多到要排隊渣，我地係唔做違法既事架！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和平請願，安全第一 <br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n現場會有500支英國旗免費派發。 用完記得拎返屋企唔好四圍棄置呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n當日主題: 訴求只有兩個: <br />\n 1. 對中國無視聯合聲明採取行動；<br />\n 2. 承認一國兩制遭受破壞；<br />\n</span></span><br />\nP.S. 呢日&quot;BNO平權&quot;唔係主題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係英領門口自發請願，915, 12:00, 英領見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2點打後 銅鑼灣自由活動</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n留意返：聽日英領我地係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對和理非<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n絕對和理非</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以下請注意: </span></strong>"},{"pid":"226177a8a86ff7ac102b53cfdd4ada2